          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/html": "<div style='width:100%;height:100vh;display:flex;flexDirection:column;margin:0;padding:0;minHeight:0'><div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 0rem'><div style='width:100%;margin:0;padding:0'><div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 1rem'><div style='margin:0;padding:0;lineHeight:0'><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Premise:</strong> You wake up one morning to discover you can understand and speak with animals, but only when wearing a specific, ridiculously patterned sock.</span></span></div><div style='width:100%;flexWrap:wrap;justifyContent:flex-start;alignItems:center;margin:0;padding:0;marginTop:-8px'><div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: row;justify-content: space-between;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 10rem'><marimo-ui-element object-id='iLit-0' random-id='cfd97a49-d8bc-3ece-028a-806fe95aac39'><marimo-button data-initial-value='0' data-label='&quot;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents&#92;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;paragraph&#92;&quot;&gt;Generate next paragraph&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;' data-kind='&quot;neutral&quot;' data-disabled='false' data-full-width='false'></marimo-button></marimo-ui-element><marimo-ui-element object-id='iLit-1' random-id='9bde8ecc-a1b5-e541-c1b3-fad545a97e21'><marimo-button data-initial-value='0' data-label='&quot;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents&#92;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;paragraph&#92;&quot;&gt;Append to story&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;' data-kind='&quot;neutral&quot;' data-disabled='false' data-full-width='false'></marimo-button></marimo-ui-element><marimo-ui-element object-id='iLit-2' random-id='19c65a4f-c7a1-03a5-8bb5-11c232104974'><marimo-button data-initial-value='0' data-label='&quot;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents&#92;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;paragraph&#92;&quot;&gt;Discard draft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;' data-kind='&quot;neutral&quot;' data-disabled='false' data-full-width='false'></marimo-button></marimo-ui-element></div></div></div></div><div style='margin:0;padding:1;flex:1 1 auto;minHeight:25'><marimo-ui-element object-id='ZHCJ-0' random-id='66d1c92e-fc6b-00eb-04cf-512af181d641'><marimo-text-area data-initial-value='&quot;The alarm blared its usual unwelcome greeting at 6:00 AM. You slapped it silent, groaning as you wrestled yourself out of bed. As you reached for your socks, something felt... different. Today, you chose the socks - a kaleidoscope of neon flamingos on a Hawaiian beach - purely by accident. Stepping into them was like stepping into a new reality, because the moment your toes were encased in that garish fabric, your cat, Mr. Snuggles, started complaining about the quality of his tuna.&quot;' data-label='&quot;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents&#92;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&#92;&quot;paragraph&#92;&quot;&gt;Story&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;' data-placeholder='&quot;&quot;' data-disabled='false' data-debounce='true' data-full-width='true' data-rows='25'></marimo-text-area></marimo-ui-element></div><div style='margin:0;padding:0;width:100%'><div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 0rem'><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"></span></div></div></div></div>"
